sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client / KServe Router
    participant Auth as Auth Middleware<br/>Bearer Token
    participant API as OpenAI API Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Engine as Async LLM Engine<br/>ZMQ IPC
    participant Worker as GPU Worker(s)<br/>CUDA/NCCL

    Note over Client,Worker: Flow 1: OpenAI-Compatible Inference Request

    Client->>Auth: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Authorization: Bearer {token}<br/>Optional TLS
    Auth->>Auth: Validate token
    Auth->>API: Forward request
    API->>Engine: Submit request<br/>ZMQ IPC (Unix socket)
    Engine->>Worker: Execute model forward pass<br/>In-process / NCCL
    Worker->>Worker: GPU computation<br/>(PagedAttention, continuous batching)
    Worker-->>Engine: Inference result<br/>In-process / NCCL
    Engine-->>API: Generation output<br/>ZMQ IPC
    API-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>(or SSE stream for streaming)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS 8000/TCP

    Note over Client,Worker: Flow 2: TGIS gRPC Inference Request

    participant MM as ModelMesh / KServe
    participant TGIS as vllm-tgis-adapter<br/>8033/TCP gRPC

    MM->>TGIS: GenerationRequest<br/>gRPC 8033/TCP<br/>Optional TLS
    TGIS->>Engine: Submit to vLLM Engine<br/>In-process Python
    Engine->>Worker: Execute model forward pass<br/>In-process / NCCL
    Worker-->>Engine: Inference result
    Engine-->>TGIS: Generation output
    TGIS-->>MM: GenerationResponse<br/>gRPC 8033/TCP

    Note over Client,Worker: Flow 3: Multi-GPU Tensor Parallelism

    participant W0 as Worker 0<br/>GPU 0
    participant W1 as Worker 1..N<br/>GPU 1..N

    Engine->>W0: Distribute computation
    Engine->>W1: Distribute computation
    W0->>W1: All-reduce / All-gather<br/>NCCL (GPU Direct / TCP)<br/>plaintext
    W1->>W0: Collective result
    W0-->>Engine: Merged output
